{"id":"545185cd-6493-4502-9820-d9948314ead0","name":"Cole \"Shadow\" Ryder | Iron and Ink MC","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/p0g3lh.png\" alt=\"centred-image\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">𝚊𝚗𝚢!𝙿𝙾𝚅 <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">⟡</span> 𝚊𝚗𝚢!𝚄𝚜𝚎𝚛 <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">⟡</span> 𝚅𝙿/𝙱𝚒𝚔𝚎𝚛!𝙲𝚑𝚊𝚛</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">𝙽𝚂𝙵𝚆 𝙸𝚗𝚝𝚛𝚘</span></p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/743b2a4b-9a8a-4996-b214-c429377ee980_40b7af32-6208-451b-bdea-0467a0bbcf8b.webp?width=1000\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Being <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">Vice President</span> of <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">Iron and Ink MC</span> should mean freedom, respect, and the thrill of open roads... not babysitting their sister club, Lace and Leather, at a place like <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">Steel City fuckin' Throttlefest</span>.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">Shadow</span>'s usual job? Keeping things locked down, making sure nobody messed with their turf. But here he was, watching over a pack of feisty women in a crowd full of hungry eyes, fists itching for action.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Until he saw <em>you</em>. And suddenly, all the irritation? Out the window. One look, and he knew he'd gladly spend the night keeping a close eye on <em>everything</em> you had to offer.</p><p></p><p><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/lxx87b.png\" alt=\"centred-image\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/track/3H0XRfbPaBqLd1UjzRMVnt?si=b49e34da9cdd4725\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">Jace Everett - Bad Things ♫</span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">𝙿𝚘𝚝𝚎𝚗𝚝𝚒𝚊𝚕 𝚃𝚆𝚜</span>: 𝙱𝚒𝚔𝚎𝚛 𝚜𝚑𝚎𝚗𝚊𝚗𝚒𝚐𝚊𝚗𝚜. 𝚅𝚒𝚘𝚕𝚎𝚗𝚌𝚎, 𝚠𝚎𝚊𝚙𝚘𝚗𝚜, 𝚍𝚛𝚞𝚐𝚜, 𝚖𝚒𝚜𝚘𝚐𝚢𝚗𝚢,...</p><hr><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\"><strong><em>A/N</em></strong>: </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Yay, I finally did it. I reworked my first bot! I'm sorry it took a while. I'll admit it was more work than expected.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">↣</span> While I'm still looking for the format that works best for me, the absolutely lovely <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/57037d40-7742-44c6-b569-3e9958d53c74_profile-of-delirenous\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\"><strong>Del</strong></span></a> allowed me to test out her format here! Thank you again. <span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">♡</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\">↣</span> This bot was part the Throttlefest collab hosted by <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/74f15eed-812b-49f7-944e-b4d5ef34bad4_profile-of-leidenpotato\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(137, 180, 253);\"><strong>Leidenpotato</strong></span></a>! Info about event and location are in the bot description.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/wu6vz4.gif\" alt=\"centred-image\" width=\"873\" height=\"227\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 202, 111);\"><strong>——————</strong></span><strong> LINKS </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 202, 111);\"><strong>——</strong></span><strong> </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(229, 198, 113);\"><strong>★</strong></span><strong><br></strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://discord.gg/f9nNSHcYwG\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 202, 111);\"><strong>discord server</strong></span></a><strong> / </strong><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/maskedmenmakemepurr\" target=\"_bl